
---
import ConnectWallet from "../components/ConnectWallet";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>AmicBridge – A private bridge between borrowers, lenders and business partners</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="AmicBridge is a private peer-to-peer network. We connect borrowers, lenders and business partners using modern Web3 wallets."
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f5f5f7;
        --surface: #ffffff;
        --border: #e5e7eb;
        --text-main: #111827;
        --text-sub: #4b5563;
        --text-muted: #6b7280;
        --primary: #2563eb;
        --primary-hover: #1d4ed8;
        --radius-lg: 12px;
        --radius-pill: 999px;
        --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
        --max-width: 1040px;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text",
          sans-serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #e0ecff 0, #f5f5f7 55%);
        color: var(--text-main);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      main {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: var(--max-width);
        padding: 32px 16px 48px;
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 32px 24px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.25);
      }

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .card {
          padding: 40px 40px;
        }

        .hero-layout {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 2.1fr) minmax(0, 1.4fr);
          gap: 40px;
          align-items: center;
        }
      }

      .badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 11px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
        background: rgba(239, 246, 255, 0.9);
        color: #1d4ed8;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 36px);
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-sub);
        max-width: 540px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .pill-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 22px;
      }

      .pill {
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.6);
        padding: 5px 11px;
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      }

      .btn-primary {
        background: var(--primary);
        color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
        border: none;
        padding: 10px 18px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        cursor: pointer;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35);
        transition: background 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease,
          box-shadow 0.15s ease;
      }

      .btn-primary:disabled {
        opacity: 0.75;
        cursor: default;
        box-shadow: none;
      }

      .btn-primary:hover:not(:disabled) {
        background: var(--primary-hover);
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.38);
      }

      .side-panel {
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px dashed rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.7);
        padding: 18px 18px 16px;
        background: radial-gradient(
            circle at 0 0,
            rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08),
            transparent 60%
          ),
          #f9fafb;
      }

      .side-title {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .side-text {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-sub);
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .side-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding-left: 0;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .side-list li {
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 28px;
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .section h2 {
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .section p {
        color: var(--text-sub);
      }

      .disclaimer {
        margin-top: 24px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        background: #fffbeb;
        border: 1px solid #fbbf24;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #92400e;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="hero-layout">
          <section>
            <div class="badge">
              <span>Early access</span>
              <span>•</span>
              <span>Private P2P network</span>
            </div>

            <h1>AmicBridge connects borrowers, lenders and partners using Web3 wallets.</h1>

            <p class="subtitle">
              A private peer-to-peer bridge for business lending, personal credit lines
              and investment deals — without a traditional bank in the middle.
            </p>

            <div class="pill-row">
              <div class="pill">Connect your wallet</div>
              <div class="pill">Discover lending opportunities</div>
              <div class="pill">Track repayments on-chain</div>
            </div>

            <section class="section">
              <h2>Start here</h2>
              <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                Connect a Web3 wallet (or a hardware wallet via MetaMask) to identify
                yourself on-chain and prepare for future lending and borrowing flows.
              </p>
              <ConnectWallet client:load />
            </section>
          </section>

          <aside class="side-panel">
            <p class="side-title">How funds will work</p>
            <p class="side-text">
              In the full version, AmicBridge will coordinate on-chain lending deals
              between private parties. Wallets hold your funds; smart contracts or
              agreements define the terms.
            </p>
            <ul class="side-list">
              <li>• Wallets stay in your control</li>
              <li>• No seed phrases are ever typed into the website</li>
              <li>• Hardware wallets (Ledger, Trezor, etc.) supported via Web3 wallets</li>
              <li>• Transparency on who owes what, backed by on-chain records</li>
            </ul>
          </aside>
        </div>

        <div class="disclaimer">
          <strong>Experimental phase.</strong>
          &nbsp;AmicBridge is under active development and not a finished lending
          product. Do not send large amounts of money. Always double-check wallet
          addresses and never share your 12/24-word recovery phrase with anyone —
          this website will never ask for it.
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
